OL,4,Ccompensation for fake injury from
OL,5,Cmilkshake cup
OL,7,FA fraudster who pretended his
OL,8,Fgranddaughter had cut her lip on a
OL,9,Fmilkshake bought from an Eastbourne
OL,10,Fcafe the day before, in a bid to try
OL,11,Fand make a claim for false
OL,12,Fcompensation has been jailed for more
OL,13,Fthan six months.
OL,15,FIan McEnroe, 62, entered the cafe in
OL,16,FTerminus Road at 7pm on 19 June, 2024,
OL,17,Fclaiming his granddaughter had ordered
OL,18,Fa milkshake the day before.
