OL,5,Cmilkshake cup
OL,7,FHe claimed that he had to spend #80
OL,8,Ffor a car valet service for split
OL,9,Fblood caused from the milkshake cup.
OL,11,FBut a member of staff at the cafe
OL,12,Frecalled that no milkshakes had been
OL,13,Fserved the day before.
OL,15,FPolice used CCTV footage to identify
OL,16,FMcEnroe, and he was charged with fraud
OL,17,Fby false representation.
OL,19,FHe was found guilty at Brighton
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court on 15 January.
