OL,7,FHe must report any incidents to police
OL,8,Fwithin 24 hours, and he is obliged to
OL,9,Fmake a declaration to any food or
OL,10,Fretail premises, in writing, that he
OL,11,Fhas been convicted for previous
OL,12,Ffraudulent refund and compensation
OL,13,Frequests.
OL,15,FSpeaking after the case, Sergeant
OL,16,FDaniel Turk said: "McEnroe has dozens
OL,17,Fof previous convictions for fraud by
OL,18,Ffalse representation, and working
OL,19,Falongside partner agencies, we were
OL,20,Fable to identify him in connection
OL,21,Fwith this investigation.
